Add NA Flag

ROSSyndicate

2023-10-31

1 add_na_flag()

Add a flag when a data point is missing.

add_na_flag <- function(df){
  df <- df %>%
    add_flag(is.na(mean), 
             "missing data")
}
  • mean = The data point of interest.
  • "missing data" = Flag descriptor inserted into the flag column.
